      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for someone looking for a reliable daily driver at an affordable price point. While the mechanical components are sound and the car starts and drives reliably, there are visible signs of age including some paint fading on the hood and minor scuffs on the bumpers. The interior shows typical wear for its age, with some staining on the upholstery and minor scratches on the dashboard plastic. It has been recently serviced and is ready for the road, but please expect a vehicle that has been well-used rather than a showroom piece.",
