    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for a fresh start and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a car back to its former glory. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it's a budget-friendly way to get your hands on a car with great potential. If you love a good restoration project, this is the one for you!",
