    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a slipping transmission and an engine that requires a major overhaul. The exterior has extensive rust on the rocker panels and severe paint oxidation throughout, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be a suitable project for a mechanic or a donor for parts, but it is not currently roadworthy.",
